body: I was never a fan of Zessica, but fucking Hisasi made me love her.
I had no idea what this series is or who these characters are, but loved this regardless because Hisasi is a fucking god.
Yeah. Zessica so cute + hot on top of having pure vanilla overflowing love with Sora, at last she had what she wanted for so long, I love her so much I want to marry her.
